Oyo State Police Command has revealed more details on how a leader of All Progressive Congress (APC), in Ona Ara Local Government of the state, Alhaji Babatunde Oreitan was killed in his house on Wednesday afternoon. According to a statement made available to Tribune Online by the image-maker of the state Police Command, Gbenga Fadeyi, the late politician was killed with sharp objects in his house and was left to bleed to death. According to Fadeyi, “Alhaji Babatunde Oreitan of Ona Ara constituency was attacked by unknown assailants in his house at Oremeji, Olorunsogo area of Ibadan, his right hand and right leg veins were slit opened with sharp objects and left to bleed to death. ALSO READ: Police deny robbery attack in Akobo communities Unravel killers of our party leader, Oyo APC tells CP Appeal Court Judgement: Commissioner congratulates Bauchi… Lagos CP Odumosu to prioritise traffic management Delta Govt. proposes N389bn for 2020 “The killers are not gunmen. They did not carry arms, but only sharp objects, preferably, blade to slit his veins opened.” “The Commissioner of Police visited the scene for on the spot assessment and had directed immediate Investigation into the dastardly killing.” Fadeyi added that the “Police operatives are on the trail of the assailants for arrest and prosecution.” The remains of the late politician, it was gathered will be committed to Mother Earth this morning. SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!! STAY STRONGER, LONGER AND SATISFY MADAM LIKE NEVER BEFORE WITH THIS NATURAL SUPPLEMENTS WITH NO SIDE EFFECTS. CLICK NOW. CLICK HERE NOW TO WORK FROM HOME ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN CONVINIENCE AND GET PAID WEEKLY, DIRECTLY INTO YOUR SPECIFIED BANK ACCOUNT.REGISTRATION IS ABSOLUTELY FREE. PREMATURE EJACULATION, SMALL SIZE FINALLY CURED NATURALLY IN 2 WEEKS FOR BIGGER, LONGER, HARDER SEXIER SEX WITH NEW MAN MACHINE